<h2 class="bold font-l">Elena's Test</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Quita Moz gets a message from the flames that a darkness is rising somewhere; soon Elena will receive a big test to defeat this unknown darkness, and if she fails, she will never become queen of Avalor. </p>
</div>
